      DOUBLE PRECISION EXPVRL
C
C  THIS COMMON HOLDS A SINGLE EXPRESSION IN SORT OF A BNF FORMAT
C  SEE PGCEXP AND PGEEXP TO SEE HOW IT IS USED.
